!width="20%"| <code>&lt;em>emphasized text&lt;/em></code> 
!width="20%"| <code>&lt;code>code&lt;/code></code> 
| semantic
|-
! <code>&lt;b>bold text&lt;/b></code> 
! <code>&lt;i>italic text&lt;/i></code> 
! <code>&lt;tt>monospace text&lt;/tt></code> 
| presentational

