! {{rh}} | [[Plain Old Documentation|POD]]
|<pre>=head1 Level 1 Heading
=head2 Level 2 Heading</pre>
|-
! {{rh}} | [[Textile (markup language)|Textile]]<ref name="textile_syntax"/>,<br />Jira
|<pre>h1. Level 1 Heading
h2. Level 2 Heading
h3. Level 3 Heading
h4. Level 4 Heading
h5. Level 5 Heading
h6. Level 6 Heading</pre>
